Project Overview

This project is a professional Power BI dashboard built using a real-world credit card sales dataset. The dashboard analyzes:

Total card sales
Customer performance
Bank-wise sales
Ratings analysis
State-wise performance
Customer sentiment
Sales trends over time

The project is fully GitHub-ready and interview-ready.

