Dataset Information
Dataset Name

credit_card_sales_dataset.xlsx

Dataset Size
Total Records: 12,000
Total Columns: 11

Columns Used
Column Name	Description
Bank Name	Credit card issuing bank
Customer Name	Customer full name
Mobile Number	Customer mobile number
Card Number	Credit card number
Customer Review	Customer feedback
No of Sales of Cards	Total cards sold
Rating	Customer rating
City	Customer city
State	Customer state
Positive Mark	Positive customer score
Negative Mark	Negative customer score
